    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ihGy3",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 100,
      "name": "h1t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "1. HOME",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "AqFrA",
      "x": 410,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "h1n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "HEADER\n- Logo \"ComfyUI Studio\" on the left (HeaderBrand component)\n- No notification bell (not implemented)\n\nGREETING / HEADLINE\n- \"What do you want to create?\"\n- Subtitle: \"Choose a workflow to get started\"\n\nFLOW CARDS\n- Large tappable cards, each represents a workflow\n- Background image with dark gradient overlay for readability\n- Icon (green square badge) + title + short description\n\n1) Generate Image\n   - Icon: sparkles\n   - Tap → navigate to /generate?personaId=\n   - Creates new images from a persona + prompt via ComfyUI\n\n2) Edit Image\n   - Icon: wand-sparkles\n   - Tap → navigate to /edit\n   - Transforms existing images using qwen-edit workflow\n\nRECENT CREATIONS\n- Horizontal scroll of latest generated/edited images (max 8 items)\n- Source: getGenerations({ limit: 5 }), all images across last 5 generations\n- Tap thumbnail:\n  - generation kind = \"generation\" → /image/$generationId/$index\n  - generation kind = \"edit\" → /edit-result/$editId\n- \"See all\" → navigate to /history\n- Hidden entirely when no items available\n\nTAB BAR\n- 4 tabs: Home, Flows, History, Settings\n- Active tab: green (#3D8A5A), inactive: gray\n- Defined in ~/components/TabBar.tsx, rendered globally in __root.tsx\n- Hidden on /generating, /results/, /image/, /edit*, /dev"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "SCTEZ",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 2870,
      "name": "h2t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "2. HISTORY",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "MThjs",
      "x": 410,
      "y": 2900,
      "name": "h2n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "HEADER\n- Title \"History\" on the left\n- Search icon on the right → tap toggles search bar\n- Search: full-text search across prompts (debounce 300ms, min. 2 characters)\n- Search bar animates in/out below header\n\nFILTER CHIPS\n- Horizontal row: \"All\" + one chip per persona (dynamic)\n- \"All\" chip active by default (green background)\n- Inactive: white/muted background\n- Tap chip = filter list by personaId\n- Single select; data loaded via getPersonas()\n- Edit-kind entries shown under \"All\", not filterable by persona\n\nGENERATION LIST\n- Vertically scrollable list of HistoryCard components\n- Each card: thumbnail (64x64), title, metadata (persona name, image count, relative time), badges\n- Tap card:\n  - kind = \"generation\" → /results/$generationId\n  - kind = \"edit\" → /edit-result/$editId\n- Infinite scroll via IntersectionObserver (sentinel div at bottom)\n- Page size: 20 items; loads more when sentinel comes into view\n- Empty state: clock icon + \"No history yet\" / \"No matching results\"\n\nDATA\n- getGenerations({ personaId?, search?, page, limit: 20 })\n- getPersonas() for chip labels\n\nTAB BAR\n- \"History\" tab active (green icon + text)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "b0L01",
      "x": 830,
      "y": 2870,
      "name": "h3t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "3. SETTINGS",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "ORS67",
      "x": 1240,
      "y": 2900,
      "name": "h3n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "HEADER\n- Title \"Settings\" centered\n- No back button (root tab screen)\n\nSERVER SECTION\n- Status: green dot + \"Connected\" / gray + \"Offline\"\n  Checked on demand via \"Test\" button (calls checkStatus())\n  Shows ComfyUI version from system_stats on success\n- API Key: masked (••••••••), tap → inline text input, saves on blur/Enter\n  Stored in data/settings.json via updateSettings()\n- Server URL is NOT editable here — configured via COMFYUI_URL env var\n\nDEFAULTS SECTION\n- Default CFG: tap value → numeric input (0–30, step 0.5), saves on blur/Enter\n- Default Steps: tap value → numeric input (1–150), saves on blur/Enter\n- Default Seed Mode: tap value → toggles Random ↔ Fixed inline\n- These values pre-fill Generation Setup and Edit Setup screens\n- Saved via updateSettings({ defaults: { cfg, steps, seedMode } })\n\nABOUT SECTION\n- Version: \"1.0.0\" (read-only, hardcoded)\n- ComfyUI Version: populated after successful \"Test\" connection (from system_stats)\n  Shows \"--\" until tested\n\nTAB BAR\n- \"Settings\" tab active (green)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "wRvZ5",
      "x": 1730,
      "y": 100,
      "name": "s1t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "STEP 2: WORKFLOW SETUP",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "rVPNn",
      "x": 2140,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "s1n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button on the left → back to Home (/)\n- Title \"Generation Setup\" centered\n\nSELECTED PERSONA\n- Thumbnail (64x64) + name + description\n- \"Change\" button → navigate back to /\n- Loaded via getPersona({ id: personaId }) from search param\n- If no personaId: shows \"No character selected\"\n\nASPECT RATIO\n- 4 options: 1:1, 16:9, 9:16, 4:3\n- Single select, default 1:1\n- Active = green background, inactive = surface-muted\n\nRESOLUTION\n- 3 options: 512px, 768px, 1024px\n- Single select, default 512px\n\nPROMPT\n- Multiline textarea (4 rows)\n- Placeholder: \"Describe your image...\"\n- Hint: \"Describe the scene, environment and situation\"\n- Max 500 characters (capped in onChange)\n\nSTEPS SLIDER\n- Range 1–150, default loaded from settings.defaults.steps\n- Current value shown on the right\n- Slider component from ~/components/ui\n\nSEED MODE\n- Toggle: Random / Fixed\n- If Fixed: numeric input for seed value appears below (default 42)\n- Default loaded from settings.defaults.seedMode\n\nBATCH COUNT\n- Stepper: minus / value / plus\n- Range: 1–20, default 4\n\nGENERATE BUTTON\n- Green gradient, primary CTA\n- Disabled if no persona selected or already submitting\n- Tap → prepare(params) → navigate to /generating\n- Uses GenerationContext (prepare/execute two-phase pattern)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "TaUEy",
      "x": 2560,
      "y": 100,
      "name": "s2t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "STEP 3: GENERATING",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "TgniM",
      "x": 2970,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "s2n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button on the left → cancel() + navigate to /results/$id (if partial) or / (home)\n- Title \"Generating\" centered\n- No confirmation dialog before cancel\n\nPREVIEW AREA\n- Full-width, 420px tall, edge-to-edge\n- Shows latest generated image from the batch (updates as each completes)\n- Spinner shown when no image available yet\n- Gradient overlay at bottom: black/50 → transparent\n- Text overlay: \"Generating image {currentBatchIndex} of {totalBatch}\"\n- Metadata: \"{personaName} · {aspectRatio} · {resolution}px · Steps {steps}\"\n- Progress bar (1px, primary color) at y=bottom, tracks current image step progress\n\nBATCH PROGRESS\n- Always visible (shown for all batch sizes incl. batch=1)\n- Horizontal row of thumbnails, one per batch item, flex fill_container\n- Completed: photo thumbnail + green ring + green check badge (top-right)\n- Current: surface-muted bg + green ring + spinning badge (top-right)\n- Pending: surface-muted bg, gray number centered\n- Driven by completedImages[] and currentBatchIndex from GenerationContext\n\nTIMER\n- Elapsed time shown (counts from mount)\n- Est. remaining shown once currentBatchIndex > 1\n- Format: M:SS\n\nCANCEL BUTTON\n- Ghost button, full width\n- \"Cancel Generation\" label + X icon\n- Tap → cancel() → navigate to /results/$id or /\n\nLIFECYCLE\n- On mount: if status=preparing → execute(); if status=idle → recover from sessionStorage\n- On status=completed → navigate to /results/$generationId\n- On status=idle (after timeout) → navigate to / after 1.5s"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "zJEaB",
      "x": 3390,
      "y": 100,
      "name": "s3t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "STEP 4: RESULTS GALLERY",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "U2GgA",
      "x": 3800,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "s3n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button → navigate to / (home, not back to /generating)\n- Title \"Results\" centered\n- Download icon on the right → handleDownloadAll() shortcut\n\nINFO ROW\n- \"{N} image(s) generated\" on the left\n- Status badge on the right: \"Completed\" (green) / \"Partial\" (orange) / \"Error\" (red)\n\nIMAGE GRID\n- ResultGrid component\n- 2-column grid, 12px gap, cornerRadius 16, shadow\n- Tap image → navigate to /image/$generationId/$index\n\nMETADATA BADGES\n- White rounded badges: \"{aspectRatio} · {resolution}px\", \"Steps {n}\", \"Random Seed\" or \"Seed {n}\"\n\nDOWNLOAD ALL BUTTON\n- Green gradient, primary CTA\n- Iterates all images, calls getOutputImage() + triggers download via <a> click\n- Disabled while download in progress\n\nGENERATE AGAIN BUTTON\n- White secondary button, refresh-cw icon\n- Navigate to /generate?personaId={generation.personaId}\n- Pre-fills same persona (parameters not re-filled, user re-enters them)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "gGnVB",
      "x": 4220,
      "y": 100,
      "name": "s4t",
      "fill": "#1A1918",
      "content": "STEP 5: IMAGE DETAIL",
      "fontFamily": "Outfit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "letterSpacing": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "KqczY",
      "x": 4630,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "s4n",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button → navigate to /results/$generationId\n- Title: \"Image {currentIndex+1} of {totalImages}\" (or \"Image\" if single)\n- Share icon on the right → navigator.share() or copies URL to clipboard\n\nIMAGE CAROUSEL\n- shadcn/ui Carousel component, height 340px, cornerRadius 20, shadow\n- Swipe left/right to navigate images in the batch\n- All images loaded in parallel via getOutputImage()\n- Dot indicators shown when totalImages > 1 (active dot = wider, green)\n- Current index tracked via carouselApi.on('select')\n\nTITLE\n- Derived from prompt: first 40 chars + \"…\" or full prompt if shorter\n- Falls back to \"Untitled\" if no prompt\n\nRELATIVE TIME\n- \"Generated just now\" / \"{N}m ago\" / \"{N}h ago\" / \"{N}d ago\" / date\n\nMETADATA BADGES\n- Green rounded badges: \"{aspectRatio} · {resolution}px\", \"Steps {n}\", seed info\n\nPROMPT CARD\n- White card, tap → copy prompt to clipboard\n- Shows \"Copied!\" toast for 2 seconds\n\nDOWNLOAD BUTTON\n- Green gradient, primary CTA\n- Downloads currently visible image (currentIndex)\n- Disabled until image URL is loaded\n\nUSE AS INPUT BUTTON\n- White secondary, image-plus icon\n- Navigate to /generate?personaId={generation.personaId}\n- Does not pre-fill prompt or other params"
    },
