    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "qq2qZ",
      "x": 1310,
      "y": 1530,
      "name": "s1note",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- HeaderBack component → back to / (home)\n- Title \"Edit Image\" centered\n\nUPLOAD ZONE\n- UploadZone component (dashed border, upload icon)\n- Title: \"Upload Image\" / \"Uploading...\" while in progress\n- Hint: \"Tap to select from your device\"\n- Formats: \"JPG, PNG, WEBP · Max 10 MB\"\n- Tap → hidden file input (<input type=file accept=image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp>)\n- On file selected → POST /api/upload-image (FormData)\n  If success → navigate to /edit-setup?image=&subfolder=&type=\n  If error → console.error (no user-facing toast currently)\n\nDIVIDER\n- TextDivider component: \"or choose recent\"\n- Only shown when recentImages.length > 0\n\nRECENT IMAGES LIST\n- RecentImageCard components, vertical list\n- Source: getRecentImages({ limit: 10 }) from src/server/edits.ts\n- Each card: thumbnail (loaded async) + filename + formatted date\n- Tap card → navigate to /edit-setup?image=&subfolder=&type=\n- Section hidden entirely when no recent images\n- Sorted by most recent first"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "dhj6J",
      "x": 2140,
      "y": 1530,
      "name": "s2note",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button on the left → back to /edit\n- Title \"Edit Setup\" centered\n\nSELECTED IMAGE PREVIEW\n- Thumbnail (64x64, cornerRadius 16) + filename + \"Source image\" label\n- \"Change\" button → navigate back to /edit\n- Image loaded via getOutputImage({ filename, subfolder, type }) from search params\n\nEDIT PROMPT\n- Multiline textarea (4 rows)\n- Placeholder: \"Describe the edit you want to make...\"\n- Hint: \"Describe what changes to apply to the image\"\n- Max 500 characters (capped in onChange)\n- No aspect ratio or resolution controls (not used by qwen-edit workflow)\n\nSTEPS SLIDER\n- Range 1–150, default 10 (workflow-specific, not from settings)\n- Slider component from ~/components/ui\n\nCFG SCALE SLIDER\n- Range 1–20, step 0.5, default 1 (workflow-specific)\n- Controls how closely the edit follows the prompt\n\nSEED MODE\n- Default loaded from settings.defaults.seedMode\n- Toggle: Random / Fixed\n- If Fixed: numeric input for seed value appears (default 42)\n\nBATCH COUNT\n- Stepper: minus / value / plus\n- Range: 1–8, default 1\n\nSTART EDITING BUTTON\n- Green gradient, primary CTA\n- Disabled if no image or already submitting\n- Tap → prepare(params) → navigate to /editing\n- Uses EditContext (prepare/execute two-phase pattern)"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "k2eOZ",
      "x": 2970,
      "y": 1530,
      "name": "s3note",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button (HeaderBack) → cancel() + navigate to /edit-result/$editId (if partial) or / (home)\n- Title \"Editing\" centered\n- No confirmation dialog before cancel\n\nPREVIEW AREA\n- Full-width, 420px tall, edge-to-edge\n- Background: source image (always shown as base)\n- When source visible but no result yet: dark overlay (60% opacity) on top\n- When result image available: shows result image directly (no overlay)\n- Spinner shown when neither source nor result is loaded yet\n- Text overlay: \"Editing image {currentBatchIndex} of {totalBatch}\"\n- Metadata: \"Steps {activeParams.steps}\"\n- Progress bar (primary color) at bottom, tracks current step progress\n\nEDIT PROGRESS\n- Section label: \"Edit Progress\"\n- Shown only when totalBatch > 1\n- Horizontal row of thumbnails (72×72px), one per batch item\n- Completed: photo thumbnail + green ring + check badge (top-right)\n- Current: surface-muted bg + green ring + spinning badge (top-right)\n- Pending: surface-muted bg, gray number centered\n- Driven by completedImages[] and currentBatchIndex from EditContext\n\nTIMER\n- Elapsed time (counts from mount)\n- Est. remaining shown once currentBatchIndex > 1\n- Format: M:SS\n\nCANCEL BUTTON\n- Ghost button, full width\n- \"Cancel Edit\" label + X icon\n- Tap → cancel() → navigate to /edit-result/$editId or /\n\nLIFECYCLE\n- On mount: if status=preparing → execute(); if status=idle → recover from sessionStorage\n- On status=completed → navigate to /edit-result/$editId\n- On status=idle (after timeout) → navigate to / after 1.5s"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "lUcP0",
      "x": 3800,
      "y": 1530,
      "name": "s4note",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "NAVIGATION\n- Back button → navigate to / (home)\n- Title \"Result\" centered\n- Download icon on the right → download currently selected result image\n\nSTATUS ROW\n- Badge on the left: \"Edit completed\" (green) / \"Partially completed\" (white) / \"Error\" (white)\n- Steps info on the right: \"{steps} steps\"\n\nBEFORE / AFTER COMPARISON\n- ComparisonSlider component (react-compare-slider), height 380px, cornerRadius 20\n- LEFT side: source image (\"Before\")\n- RIGHT side: selected result image (\"After\")\n- Drag handle to reveal more of either side\n- Default position: center (50/50 split)\n- Shows spinner while images are loading\n\nVARIANT THUMBNAILS\n- Shown only when resultImages.length > 1\n- Horizontal row of thumbnails (72×72px), one per result\n- Selected: photo thumbnail + green ring\n- Others: surface-muted bg, number centered, gray border\n- Tap thumbnail → setSelectedIndex(i) → updates comparison slider\n- Position: between comparison slider and meta badges\n\nMETADATA BADGES\n- White rounded badges: \"Steps {n}\"\n- Read-only edit parameter info\n\nSAVE EDITED IMAGE BUTTON\n- Green gradient, primary CTA\n- Saves currently selected result image (download via data URL)\n- Disabled until result image is loaded\n\nEDIT AGAIN BUTTON\n- White secondary button, pencil icon\n- Navigates to /edit-setup with same source image params pre-filled"
    },
