    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "4bTvw",
      "x": 1310,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "s1note",
      "width": 380,
      "height": 844,
      "content": "⚠️ SCREEN NOT IMPLEMENTED\n\nThis screen was planned as a \"Choose Character\" step before Generation Setup,\nbut was removed from the current implementation.\n\nCURRENT FLOW\n- Home → /generate?personaId={id}\n- personaId is empty by default (no character pre-selected)\n- Generation Setup shows \"No character selected\" if personaId is missing\n- There is no dedicated character picker screen\n\nCHARACTERS / PERSONAS\n- Stored in data/personas.json\n- CRUD via server functions in src/server/personas.ts\n- Referenced in Generation Setup and History filter chips\n\nFUTURE CONSIDERATION\n- Could be added as a modal or a dedicated /personas route\n- Would navigate to /generate?personaId={id} on selection"
    },
